message.body: I think pre prom is gonna be at my house
What is pre prom?
It's just like getting dressed and taking pictures and traveling to prom together
Ok what time were you thinking?
Prom starts at 6? Probably 4ish. Also did you want to go to the after party in queens?
Prom starts at 7:30 lol , and ill be by ur house by 6:30
Lol check ur ticket :p
Oops! You're right. Well my house is close to Chelsea piers so we can either walk or take a cab. It will probably start at 5 or 5:30 so come then!
Why so early? I don't think ill be able to make it intime , ill try my best but I'm not sure ill be there by 5:30
Like 6ish hopefully
Ok! Early so we have enough time for everyone to arrive and get ready and leave together on time. We will drop off our bags for the hamptons there and go back to pick them up later
I'm getting my hair and makeup done in brooklyn getting dressed at my casa and comin over
Ok that sounds like a good plan, I really don't know what we should do after prom , maybe go to to the party in queens or we can like walk around the city
And like get pancakes!!! Or waffles lol
Yeah we will have time to go to queens or take a walk if we want, or just go home and crash. Pancakes in the morning are a must
Awesomee !!!! As long as I get pancakes were good
Tuxedo acquired!
Good!
Ok. Ooooh shiny
